has_equalizers_of_has_pullbacks_and_bina:
-- This is not an instance, as it is not always how one wants to construct equalizers!
/-- Any category with pullbacks and binary products, has equalizers. -/
theorem has_equalizers_of_has_pullbacks_and_binary_products [HasBinaryProducts C] [HasPullbacks C] : HasEqualizers C :=
  {
    has_limit := fun F =>
      HasLimit.mk
        { cone := equalizerCone F
          is_limit := equalizerConeIsLimit F } }
#align has_equalizers_of_has_pullbacks_and_binary_products has_equalizers_of_has_pullbacks_and_binary_products
